{"tid":1635222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日已經俾休息撚全勝","createTime":"2019-10-07T12:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T14:34:54.000Z","uid":47659,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"64e7074b6ffcd3003e8fe0fd9a3a06638c06e24f","tid":1635222,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:33:19.000Z","msg":"唔想輸就出黎啊"},{"pid":"6637c7d24ed327bb768a9d8461b60ca15ad29e66","tid":1635222,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:34:19.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上為節錄內容，覺得有道理請睇全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"},{"pid":"5e186ee37c5bbfa1cb011938047bb1ee22a39599","tid":1635222,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:36:25.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但勇和齊上齊落唔撚得？"},{"pid":"e7407cfaeb76637d98061cf9bdd566579a37593b","tid":1635222,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:36:37.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"823591cd6d90963eb3a2090b8021832943351e59","tid":1635222,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:36:53.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"d7764cc0af26367761b3523c43c54caf95fe4e02","tid":1635222,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:37:43.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"c777a659adb4dcbcc3e32fdd714460b49096124f","tid":1635222,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:38:34.000Z","msg":"之鋒一出聲，馬上踢爆分化五毛所謂休息唔裝修既風向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4f01da344ef38f03388c81a28ace8cd55dd744f4","tid":1635222,"uid":86119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:39:17.000Z","msg":"真係好少人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6d1c3977be3cb7e2f30bb904304a78c6545773","tid":1635222,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:39:29.000Z","msg":"和理有好<br />\n<br />\n勇武又好<br />\n<br />\n左膠都好<br />\n<br />\n最緊要有人"},{"pid":"4d9f934af191231fb9f56767a514d6788be2eec1","tid":1635222,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d1af311b1f60906b17cf488e64d0a06a6a9f2ba","tid":1635222,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:27:23.000Z","msg":"之鋒一出聲，馬上踢爆分化五毛所謂休息唔裝修既風向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e7bb94795580e068c0e005d428e90dfb86fdd1bf","tid":1635222,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}